title: How do I close pages in the built-in browser?
answer: On the Browser screen, select![](http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=96876) or ![](http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=96877) to display thumbnails of all the pages that are open. Touch ![](http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=96878) to close the pages that are not needed.
keywords: close web page, Internet Explorer, browser, web pages, close, preloaded browser
